Events that occurred on 5 December.

content.title: On Earth
content.content:
1906 - Actor Otto Preminger is born.
1953 - Actor Christopher Guard is born.
1964 - The ninth episode of the Princess-serialization of The Hobbit is published.
1985 - Artist Matěj Čadil is born.
2002 - The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers premieres at Ziegfeld Theatre, in New York City.

content.title: In Arda
content.content:
T.A. 3018:
Frodo and Samwise rest in Rivendell and prepare for their quest to destroy the One Ring.
